# zarya Repository Context

This is a monorepo for the **zarya** community platform. Apps live under `apps/`. The current MVP is `apps/zarya-tg/` — a Telegram Mini App for community event management.

Use `apps/zarya-tg/docs/prd.md` as the canonical source for product scope, user stories, and acceptance criteria. Use `apps/zarya-tg/docs/decisions/` for all architectural and product decisions. Use `apps/zarya-tg/docs/tickets/` for AC tickets with Human summaries. Use `process/ai-factory/` for the portable AI-Factory playbook. Use `apps/zarya-tg/frontend/` for all React + TypeScript Telegram Mini App code. Use `apps/zarya-tg/backend/` for all FastAPI and aiogram bot code. Use `apps/zarya-tg/docs/tasks.md` to track and update the current task backlog.

## MVP Scope for zarya-tg (do not add features outside this list without a decision record)

Event browsing (chronological, all future events, with cover images), event registration and cancellation, calendar export (.ics file), admin interface via Telegram bot commands, Russian-only interface.

## Out of Scope for MVP

Access codes and circle-tier events, user profiles, automated notifications, participant list visibility, English localization.

## Stack

Frontend: React 18 + TypeScript + Telegram Web App SDK. Backend: FastAPI (Python 3.11) + aiogram. Database: PostgreSQL (Railway). Deployment: Railway.com (Docker).
